      "description": "This protocol includes six questions of perceived effectiveness from the Perceived Effectiveness of Cessation Advertisements study to assess whether perceived effectiveness for anti-tobacco ads are causally related to tobacco-related behaviors and outcomes. Participants of the study are asked to pro",
